    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for any dark ornamental wood derived from various tropical American trees, especially of the genus Jacaranda, the species Dalbergia nigra (Brazilian rosewood), or the genus Peltogyne.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
